data.description: Perfect location!!  Minutes to North Charleston!  This home has all new windows in the back, new roof, newer HVAC, and new floors!!  Great lot with a fenced in back yard!  You will enter into the living room where you have plenty of room!  The large eat in kitchen has tons of cabinets and countertops!!  Laundry room is just off the kitchen.  Down the hall you have a full bath, two guest rooms, and a owner's suite with a private bath!  The back yard has 2 sheds and large deck for all of your entertainment needs!
